NEW DELHI, THE 5TH JUNE, 1986.
15 JYAISTHA 1908 (S).
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from
th June, 1986 :-
(a) Shri Bansi Lal, relinquished the Office of the
Minister of Transport;
(b) Shri Rajiv Gandhi, Prime Minister assumed the
Office of the Minister of Transport, also till alternate
arrangements are made; and
(c) Shri Biren Singh Engti, Deputy Minister in the
Department of Personnei and Training has been
redesignated as Deputy Minister in the Ministry
of Personnel, Public Grievances and Pensions.
